title: Don Cheadle’s First Bass Lesson was from Ron Carter // SiriusXM // Real Jazz
description:
Don Cheadle sat down with Miles Davis’ old bass player Marcus Miller during a SiriusXM Town Hall about his upcoming film “Miles Ahead”. Don get’s into a story about getting his first bass lesson from Ron Carter.
